mention is solely from generation to generation.Ð{\highlight7 <IT>}Siach Yitzchok{\highlight7 <ITC>}\par
{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <SZ6>}{\highlight7 <SUP2.5>}{\highlight7 <*16>}16{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <IT>}{\highlight7 <SZ9>}{\highlight7 <SUP0>}Psalms{\highlight7 <ITC>} 135:13.\par
